    <text>Intermediate Object to store the allocation of a Stock Order Line's
Tracked Items to a BOLOut.  This is necessary because we won't always
send all the Tracked Items for a Stock Order line in a single BOLOut.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="bol"/>
